OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis says it is wrong
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto cut sick pay for        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Funjabbed staff             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Retailer John Lewis has said all its   
OL,6, staff are entitled to full sick pay for
OL,7, Covid-related absences, regardless of  
OL,8, vaccination status, and it would not be
OL,9, "right" to differentiate.              
OL,11,FIt comes after Ocado, Next and Ikea    
OL,12,Frevealed they only pay the legal       
OL,13,Fminimum to unjabbed staff if they have 
OL,14,Fto isolate due to Covid exposure.      
OL,16,FJohn Lewis's operations director Andrew
OL,17,FMurphy said he "cast no judgement".    
OL,19,FAnd he added the firm was "not going to
OL,20,Fmake any change of this type".         
